name: Conjunctured
overview:
Conjunctured is a coworking space and creative agency located in Austin.

As a coworking space, Conjunctured provides a creative environment for entrepreneurs that encourages collaboration.

As an agency, Conjunctured is focused on helping organizations have conversations online - however that may take shape.
